OL,3,CFamily of nurse who died after
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosis say she was let down by
OL,5,Cthe NHS
OL,7,FThe family of a nurse who died days
OL,8,Fafter being misdiagnosed with
OL,9,Findigestion say she was let down by
OL,10,Fthe NHS when she needed it most.
OL,12,FPaula Ivers was found dead by her 9
OL,13,Fyear old daughter after being sent
OL,14,Fhome from Tameside Hospital, Greater
OL,15,FManchester, in March 2024 and told to
OL,16,Fbuy a bottle of Gaviscon.
OL,18,FShe had been a paediatric nurse for
OL,19,Fmore than 24 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
