OL,3,CFamily of nurse who died after
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosis say she was let down by
OL,5,Cthe NHS
OL,7,FHer sister Lesley Ivers, also a nurse,
OL,8,Ftold her inquest: "It is a cruel irony
OL,9,Fthat Paula was a fierce advocate and
OL,10,Fdefender of the NHS, yet when she
OL,11,Fneeded it most, she was let down in
OL,12,Fthe worst way possible."
OL,14,FManchester South Coroners' Court heard
OL,15,Fthat the 47-year-old had gone to the
OL,16,Faccident and emergency department
OL,17,Fafter experiencing crushing chest
OL,18,Fpains which she described to her
OL,19,Fpartner as being worse than childbirth.
OL,21,FShe was sent home the same day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
