OL,5,Cthe NHS
OL,7,FHer inquest heard that three days
OL,8,Flater she was found collapsed on her
OL,9,Fbedroom floor by her 9-year-old
OL,10,Fdaughter.
OL,12,FA post mortem revealed she died from
OL,13,Fan aortic dissection, a time-critical
OL,14,Fmedical emergency caused by a tear in
OL,15,Fthe aorta.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
