OL,3,CFamily of nurse who died after
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosis say she was let down by
OL,5,Cthe NHS
OL,7,FPaula's family believe her death was
OL,8,Fas a result of poor care at the
OL,9,Fhospital in Ashton-under-Lyne and that
OL,10,Fthere were numerous failings and
OL,11,Fmissed opportunities to correctly
OL,12,Fdiagnose her.
OL,14,FThe court heard Dr Osama Ahmed, senior
OL,15,Fclinician in the emergency department
OL,16,Fon the day she went to hospital,
OL,17,Fdecided Ms Ivers was low risk and
OL,18,Fcould be sent to Same Day Emergency
OL,19,FCare (SDEC) despite not examining her
OL,20,Fhimself or knowing her family history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
