OL,3,CFamily of nurse who died after
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosis say she was let down by
OL,5,Cthe NHS
OL,7,FThe inquest learned that Paula's
OL,8,Ffather had died from a cardiac arrest
OL,9,Fin his early 40s.
OL,11,FDr Ahmed also overruled the findings
OL,12,Fof her ECG which had been reported as
OL,13,Fabnormal.
OL,15,FThe court heard Paula was not given a
OL,16,FCT scan, one of the most common ways
OL,17,Fto diagnose an aortic dissection.
OL,19,FDr Ahmed told the court he now accepts
OL,20,Fthat Paula wasn't low risk and
OL,21,Fshouldn't have gone to SDEC.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
