OL,7,FIn his opinion, aortic dissection was
OL,8,Fnot a common condition, he said.
OL,10,FHe added that hospital staff were a
OL,11,Flot more aware of the condition since
OL,12,Fthe case.
OL,14,FThe coroner said he had to make a
OL,15,F"difficult decision" to adjourn the
OL,16,Finquest until June 2026 despite
OL,17,Fknowing the distress that the delay
OL,18,Fwould cause Paula's family.
