OL,7,FSome of the witnesses would struggle
OL,8,Fto attend the inquest due to staff
OL,9,Fshortages caused by this week's
OL,10,Fdoctors strikes, he explained.
OL,12,FMs Ivers' family hope the case will
OL,13,Fraise awareness of aortic dissection
OL,14,Famong medical professionals and the
OL,15,Fpublic.
